{"tid":591863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有口話人！冇口話自己！","createTime":"2018-03-13T23:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T13:01:18.000Z","uid":135492,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa83c91a965223f10fb522ba7b900475c37e4d07","tid":591863,"uid":135492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T23:41:55.000Z","msg":"好好笑，有個fd自己次次叫嘅男仔fd買野食，雖然係十幾二十蚊，但係就沒次都唔俾翻錢。而自己又去串其他男仔幫人買野食，但至少其他女仔每次都有俾錢，仲要係有多出黎。好心了，你有咩資格話「人地當你兵渣」「你又幫人買野啊」呢d說話。甘你當幫你買野食嘅男仔係咩啊？問過曬班fd，真係好離譜，憑咩要次次請你食野。佢屋企人賺錢唔係俾你用！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇方法可以令個女嘅唔再叫人幫佢買野食，或者令佢知道要俾返錢？我地一班兄弟睇唔過眼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1256763a4e9a8dd8cb5006a178feadc9bcdac578","tid":591863,"uid":135492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T23:43:36.000Z","msg":"sor for 19999"},{"pid":"334ebf1f80f5fa53005ce20ae331f964604d0cf4","tid":591863,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T23:45:57.000Z","msg":"Lm 樓主個friend係唔係肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571130251e5c952c63b5e1e80fe228debc550114","tid":591863,"uid":135492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"334ebf1f80f5fa53005ce20ae331f964604d0cf4","tid":591863,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T23:45:57.000Z","msg":"Lm 樓主個friend係唔係肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T23:47:07.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ea4ed856e1ed89c878ca6eca739f2d5fa9921e","tid":591863,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:56:55.000Z","msg":"毒撚群中有隻雞"},{"pid":"276d1c17589e6e4d80b5978d8d38410222aeeca4","tid":591863,"uid":135492,"